                        h2 Relaxed Coastal Comfort at The Westin Resort & Spa Los Cabos
                        h3 A Brief Overview and Location
                        p The Westin Resort & Spa Los Cabos is a beachfront resort located along the scenic Tourist Corridor between Cabo San Lucas and San José del Cabo, Baja California Sur, Mexico, where the desert meets the sea. Perched on the shores of the Sea of Cortez, the hotel offers a tranquil setting with sweeping ocean views, warm sunshine and refreshing sea breezes — ideal for travelers seeking a relaxed yet sophisticated coastal escape. The property is roughly 25 – 30 minutes by car from Los Cabos International Airport, making it easily accessible for both short stays and extended vacations.
                        p The resort’s architecture and vibrant design reflect the energy of Baja, with bright colors and open spaces that take full advantage of the natural surroundings. Its beachfront location provides guests with scenic vistas and opportunities to enjoy seaside relaxation alongside leisure activities.

        section.features
            .container
                .row
                    .col-12
                        h3 What Makes It Special
                        p Comfortable Accommodations with Ocean Views
                        p Guest rooms and suites at The Westin Resort & Spa Los Cabos are designed for comfort and convenience, many offering balconies or terraces with views of the Sea of Cortez. Interiors feature contemporary furnishings and thoughtful amenities that enhance a restful stay.
                        p Beachfront Pool and Outdoor Spaces
                        p The property features multiple outdoor pools and lounge areas where guests can relax under the sun, take in ocean panoramas, or sip refreshing drinks by the water’s edge. Poolside cabanas and terraces provide plenty of space to unwind.
                        p Wellness and Spa Facilities
                        p A full-service spa and wellness centre offers a range of treatments inspired by the desert and sea, helping guests relax and rejuvenate. Spa services can include massages, body treatments, hydrotherapy and more, designed to soothe both body and mind.
                        p Dining Options for Every Taste
                        p The resort’s restaurants and bars serve a mix of international and local cuisine, from casual beachfront meals to more refined dining experiences. Guests can savour fresh seafood, Mexican-inspired dishes, and refreshing beverages throughout their stay.
                        p Recreation and Leisure Activities
                        p In addition to beachside leisure, the resort offers a variety of activities such as tennis, volleyball, and excursions arranged through concierge services. Nearby golf courses and local attractions make it easy to explore the wider Los Cabos region.
                        p Family-Friendly Amenities
                        p While maintaining a relaxed atmosphere, the resort welcomes families with facilities that include pools suitable for children, outdoor play areas, and a kids club with supervised activities.
                        p Event and Business Spaces
                        p The hotel also includes venues for meetings, weddings and special occasions, with services and facilities to accommodate both intimate gatherings and larger events against a scenic coastal backdrop.

